{{Infobox person | name = Viji prakash |occupation = [[Bharata Natyam|Bharata Natyam dancer]] | image = File:Vji conducting bw flatened copy.jpg | birth_date = | birth_place = [[India]] | height = | yearsactive = | birth_name = Vijaya Lakshmi | othername = | website = {{official|http://shaktibharatanatyam.com/}} | awards = Devdasi National Award 2014, Kerala Sangeeta Nataka Academy Award 2013 }}
'''Vijaya Lakshmi Prakash''', popularly known as '''Viji Prakash,''' is an [[India]]n [[Bharata Natyam]] [[dancer]], instructor, [[choreography|choreographer]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/thehindu/fr/2005/12/30/stories/2005123002700600.htm|title=Roots intact|work=The Hindu|accessdate=31 July 2010}}</ref> and founder of the Shakti Dance Company and Shakti School of Bharata Natyam. Prakash has worked in the USA since 1976.
